                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 822.00/326.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 16, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Bombardment of Esmeraldas is threatened. Presence of the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Buffalo</hi> would prevent unnecessary destruction of life and property. I
                    again recommend that it proceed to that port.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
